OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine in
OL,7,Fplaces, most likely the east. Then the
OL,8,Frest of the night will be dry with
OL,9,Fvariable amounts of cloud, likely
OL,10,Fcloudiest in the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FIt will be dry with some
OL,13,Fsunshine breaking through the cloud.
OL,14,FCloudier in the west in the morning,
OL,15,Fsunniest across the east. Very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
